short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Your Website SEO Audit Tool by Quick2link

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Quick2Link Website Audit extension has provided audit tools. Goal for making this extension is to help any website marketer analyze either their own or a competitor's web page. 

First, click the Quick2Link extension icon to drop down the list of tools while on the page you want to audit. Under "Site Audit" tab. After that click the tool's link that you want to use to audit the page. 

Second, Click the "Tips & Trick" tab and you will get free Tips & Tricks for your website and your website SEO. You can use these trips and tricks as an audit checklist for your website and website SEO.

We love to hear your feedback and improvements required in the tool. 
We are also working on Quick2Link Pro version.

If you have any recommendations on making these tools better, feel free to reach out to us on dvlpr.in. 

Don't forget to share the tools on your network as well as mention the chrome extension link.
